}
/*
*Alternativestrategytoacostly(evenindexedsearch)tothe
*database.
*Wesearchintheschemaifwehavealreadythisintid(usingdsdb_attribute_by_attributeID_idbecause
*intherange0x800000000xBFFFFFFFF,attributeIDisaDSDB_ATTID_TYPE_INTID).
*Ifsogenerateanotherrandomvalue.
